<section sectnbr = "1D">
<servcat sctnbr = "01" scnbr = "04">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AHRAP70A1406026" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Uklanjanje i ugradnja ventila i glave motora
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A1406025">Komponente ventila i glave motora</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A1406026001">
<title>
Uklanjanje
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite sklop motora s vozila. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1406016"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite usisnu granu. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1406009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite cijev rashladne vode. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1606007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite korito ulja. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1506004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite poklopac glave motora. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1406011"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite poklopac lanca razvodnog mehanizma. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1406018"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite lanac razvodnog mehanizma. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1406023"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite bregasto vratilo ispuha i usisa. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1406013"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite ležajeve bregastih vratila.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Odvijte vijke glave motora redoslijedom prikazanim na slici pomoću 12-kutnog nasadnog ključa i uklonite ih.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A141002.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.080mm" ver = "01" gw = "189" gh = "128"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Provjerite ima li oko glave motora dijelova koje treba ukloniti ili odspojiti te uklonite ili odspojite što je potrebno.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite glavu motora s ispušnom granom. Upotrijebite dizalicu ako je potrebno.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Uklonite sljedeće komponente s glave motora ako je potrebno.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Ispušna grana: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1B06002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Brizgaljka goriva: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1706008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Venturi priključak ulja: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1406027"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Sklop termostata: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1606008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A1406026002">
<title>
Ugradnja
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A1406027">Rastavljanje i ponovo sastavljanje ventila i glave motora</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Očistite dodirne površine glave motora i bloka motora. Uklonite ulje, staro brtvilo i prašinu s dodirne površine.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Postavite zatike za centriranje (1) na blok motora.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Postavite novu brtvu glave motora (2) na blok motora.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A141004.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "43.930mm" ver = "01" gw = "150" gh = "108"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Postavite glavu motora na blok motora kako slijedi.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Prije postavljanja glave motora namjestite koljenasto vratilo u rasponu &#34;a&#34; prikazanom na slici.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Prije pritezanja vijaka glave motora zakrenite koljenasto vratilo ulijevo za 30&#176; – 90&#176; kako je prikazano na slici.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Ako ponovo koristite postojeći vijak glave motora, obavezno ga provjerite radi izobličenja. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1406030"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I7V20A141058.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "37.283mm" ver = "01" gw = "129" gh = "89"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "6" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.727in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.727in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "0.970in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
“a”:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
30&#176;
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
“b”:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
90&#176;
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Klin
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Nanesite motorno ulje na nove vijke glave motora.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Zategnite vijke glave motora (&#34;1&#34; - &#34;10&#34;) momentom pritezanja od 20 N&#183;m (2,0 kgf-m, 15,0 lb-ft) brojčanim redoslijedom kao što je prikazano pomoću 12-kutnog nasadnog ključa.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Na isti način kao u koraku b), zategnite ih momentom pritezanja od 40 N&#183;m (4,1 kgf-m, 29,5 lbf-ft).
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Zakrenite sve vijke 60&#176; redoslijedom brojeva na slici.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Ponovite korak d.
</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T1D018">
<t-part>
Vijak glave motora*
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-note>
20 N&#183;m &#8594; 40 N&#183;m &#8594; +60&#176; &#8594; +60&#176; (2,0 kgf-m &#8594; 4,0 kgf-m &#8594; +60&#176; &#8594; +60&#176;, 14,5 lbf-ft &#8594; 29,0 lbf-ft &#8594; +60&#176; &#8594;+60&#176;)
</t-note>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A141005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.647mm" ver = "02" gw = "177" gh = "127"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite bregasta vratila i podizač prema koracima od 2 do 8 odjeljka &#34;Ugradnja&#34; poglavlja 
<intxref refid = "AHRAP70A1406013">Uklanjanje i ugradnja bregastog vratila i podizača</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite lanac razvodnog mehanizma. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1406023"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite poklopac lanca razvodnog mehanizma. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1406018"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite poklopac glave motora. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1406011"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite korito ulja. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A1506004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
